42
00:01:35,139 --> 00:01:37,199
And finally, we sum all of that up.

43
00:01:37,199 --> 00:01:37,979
and then take the average.

44
00:01:37,979 --> 00:01:40,800
And that's why it's called the Mean Squared Error.

45
00:01:40,800 --> 00:01:42,460
Each step is a separate operation.

46
00:01:42,460 --> 00:01:43,850
Let's look at it in reverse.

47
00:01:43,850 --> 00:01:45,690
And a lot of the time, you'll also see this,

