102
00:03:27,500 --> 00:03:28,660
So, in this case,

103
00:03:28,660 --> 00:03:31,400
Then, MMSE is equivalent to maximum likelihood estimation.

104
00:03:31,400 --> 00:03:34,500
So, where MSE really shines is when the errors are symmetrical.

105
00:03:34,500 --> 00:03:35,500
some predictions are large,

106
00:03:35,500 --> 00:03:36,769
