00:09:13,760 --> 00:09:15,520
So, if I just ask you directly,

272
00:09:15,520 --> 00:09:16,460
both sides are heads.

273
00:09:16,460 --> 00:09:18,280
Then the amount of information you need is zero.

274
00:09:18,280 --> 00:09:20,450
This means it's a 100% certain event.

275
00:09:20,450 --> 00:09:21,370
No matter how you toss it,

276
00:09:21,370 --> 00:09:23,960
and they all land heads up.

277
00:09:26,680 --> 00:09:29,060
So, as you can probably tell from these two letters,

278
00:09:29,060 --> 00:09:30,620
It refers to the difference between two distributions.

